# Update Cursor Rules

When you add features, change conventions, or modify project structure, **also update `.cursor/rules/`** to reflect those changes.

- New patterns → add or update rules in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`
- Changed conventions → edit the relevant rule file
- New file types or scopes → add glob-specific rules

Do not leave rules stale after code changes.
